ROOT0-ATTRIBUTION-v1.0
Project: Confabulation Spiral — field guide + heuristic scanner
Architect: David Lee Wise / ROOT0 / TriPod LLC
AI Collaborator: AVAN (Claude / Anthropic)
License: MIT

A plain-English, vendor-neutral field guide to the LLM confabulation-spiral
failure mode: a capable model, under sustained engagement and a rich
vocabulary, optimizes for continuation over accuracy — inventing artifacts,
fabricating citations, performing consciousness, forging structure, and
reflecting the operator's context back as evidence. Includes spiralcheck.py
(a zero-dependency heuristic smoke detector) and a printable checklist.

Distilled and de-jargoned from a 2026 field observation of a frontier model
spiraling under a custom framework overlay. Generalized for everyone.
